# Credit Scoring & Risk Assessment

This collection focuses on **Evaluating borrower creditworthiness and modeling financial risks like probability of default.**.

## Notebooks

- 01_retail_credit_scoring_logistic_regression.ipynb
- 02_corporate_credit_risk_multiclass.ipynb
- 03_probability_of_default_estimation.ipynb
- 04_stress_testing_scenario_modeling.ipynb
- 05_loss_given_default_regression.ipynb
- 06_exposure_at_default_forecasting.ipynb
